finding a place that’s friendly, fun, sexy and above all affordable for my new project. I’ve have spend about 1,000 USD total on rent and move in and travel. rude service and /or dirty and shitty apartments but overall affordable and hard to find are: safe – $300-$400 GREEN power – $100 internet – $60 cable – $10 (in most apartments) for 30 channels water – $20 a year!

Taxi is very affordable in my experience, a 1 way trip averaging $1.00

Bus is also affordable, my basic one way is $0.25

Personally I find my basic daily cost to be $4-$5 a day for food and transport (unless I want a tasty steak and or serviced in a restaurant. But that’s NO more expensive than New York or Miami! But Ecuador also has a new line of taxi called BiciCleta , they are bikes with pedals with a seat for two where as driver peddles and passenger can take a backseat to enjoy a glass of champagne or wine

and the journey can be free (if you can’t afford it) or $0.25 not bad for downtown Quito. they also have electric missions that are safe and they bring food to you!
